<p dir="auto">Wrapped up the prototype with <a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/dfosco/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/dfosco">@dfosco</a> 🎉 We still have a few issues to address: <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="3989504288" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/github/growth-life-cycle/issues/488" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/github/growth-life-cycle/issues/488/hovercard" href="https://github.com/github/growth-life-cycle/issues/488">#488</a>, but we're going to start sharing with customers ASAP. I also put together a <a href="https://microsofteur-my.sharepoint.com/:w:/r/personal/amarilisdias_microsoft_com/Documents/Code%20quality%20Vision%20User%20research.docx?d=wf36c584b31f74a5f8eaa1c4f00b8c465&amp;csf=1&amp;web=1&amp;e=E5zIdu" rel="nofollow">code quality user research plan</a> so we can translate the user interviews into qualitative and quantitative results we can analyze to inform our next steps.</p>
